OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Fdry evening with light winds and clear
OL,7,Fspells. Turning cloudier overnight
OL,8,Fwith a few showers, these mainly in
OL,9,Feast near the coast.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FA largely cloudy day with
OL,12,Foutbreaks of showery rain possible.
OL,13,FShowers may become heavy in places
OL,14,Fthrough the afternoon. Drier in the
OL,15,Feast later. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
